The jQuery validate plugin is a popular plugin developed by JÃ¶rn Zaefferer.
The official link to the plugin: http://bassistance.de/jquery-plugins/jquery-plugin-validation/

My purpose is to provide additional methods for the validate plugin.

Multiple emails

Useful for validating a field wherein email addresses have to be separated by a comma.

Example:

HTML
<form id="formID">
<textarea class="required multiple_emails"></textarea>
<input type="submit" value="Submit">
</form>

jQuery:

$(document).ready( function(){
  $(".validate_send_mail").validate();
  $('a.send_to_more_friends').click(function() {
    $('.validate_send_mail').addClass('block');
    return false;
  });

});

